    <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
      <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="Aink417-kilavi">ituvum atu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">And this is that.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <lg xml:id="Aink417">        
<l>kārkalan taṉṟāṟ puṟavē palavuṭa</l>
<l>ṉērparan taṉavāṟ puṉamē yērkalantu</l>
<l>tātār piraca moyppap</l>
<l>pōtār kūntaṉ muyaṅkiṉa ḷemmē.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg xml:lang="en">
            <l>The rainy season has arrived.</l> 
            <l>In the woodland, ploughs, many together,</l> 
            <l>have spread out on the fields. Having [re-]gained [her] beauty,</l> 
            <l>as [bees] swarm around honey combs full of pollen,</l> 
            <l>the one with the tresses full of flowers embraced me.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </body>
